tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE client_progress (
    client_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    therapist_id INT,
    session_date DATE,
    session_duration INT,
    treatment_outcome VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE progress_data (
    progress_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    client_id UUID,
    treatment_id UUID,
    progress_date TIMESTAMP,
    progress_notes TEXT
);
